4Geeks Academy offers a Full Stack Developer Bootcamp designed to equip students with in-demand skills in technologies such as JavaScript and Python. This 18-week program includes 16 weeks of instruction plus 2 weeks dedicated to project development, with classes held three times a week and a low student-to-teacher ratio of 7:1. Participants will gain hands-on experience by building projects and can choose to study in either English or Spanish. No prior coding skills are required, making it accessible to beginners. Graduates will earn a Full-Stack Developer certificate upon completion. For more information, visit [https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/part-time-full-stack-developer](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/part-time-full-stack-developer). stop